    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: DialogueLines.Array.size
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: emotionRanges.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Si Tina to nak, okay ka lang ba? Ba\u2019t parang kabado ka?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Tina? Who's Tina?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Lumabas ka na diyan, kanina ka pa dapat gising eh.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: "So it\u2019s a woman who\u2019s behind the door. Her voice was stern
        but it doesn\u2019t seem like there was any malice, it only sounded frantic
        as if she was in a hurry. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: Tanghali na, kanina ka pa dapat gising. May sakit ka ba, Aleks? Parang
        nakakita ka ng multo
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: Sino ka? Nasaan ako?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: Si Tina, Tina Raymundo? Nandito ka sa bahay namin. Kailangan mo ba ng
        doktor?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: Raymundo?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: I looked around the kitchen outside where she stood. No wonder it felt
        a bit familiar, I was inside the Raymundo house, but it somehow feels off.
        Why does it look so new and lively?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: "Then it clicked. Tina Raymundo\u2026THE Tina Raymundo, wife of Joe
        Raymundo, mother of the house is right in front of me. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: DialogueSpeakers.Array.size
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: Tina looks at me confused as I try to piece the puzzle together.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: "Ah\u2026Aleks, siguro pagod ka pa galing sa biyahe, Hayaan muna kita,
        kailangan ko pa asikasuhin mga anak ko. Baba ka nalang kung may kailangan
        ka. Sana makikilala mo din sila ngayong bakasyon."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueSpeakers.Array.data[0]'
      value: Tina
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4967227864417536909, guid: edc20a0af6d693e40b4d8c4ed77ad50b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogueSpeakers.Array.data[1]'
